title: The Power Of The Force Of The Allmighty Dragon Through Flames And Steel
tags: 2008 animal Chiptune Metal OpenMPT PowerMetal Rock
info:
When you're bored, you do crazy shit. This is a fast done song, in an extreme power metal style mixed with chiptunes. Let's say its a mixture between Dragonforce and Machinae Supremacy in a more extreme way, still funny to hear.

ps: The song was made by using Open MODPlug Tracker.
